      "content": {
        "title": "Normal Curve Properties",
        "definition": "The normal (Gaussian) distribution is bell-shaped, symmetric about its mean μ, with spread determined by standard deviation σ.",
        "summary": "Normal curves model many natural and measurement phenomena and are fully characterized by μ and σ."
      },
